Prevent runaway execution with CPU and memory bounds:

```ts
const runtime = new NodeRuntime({
  systemDriver: createNodeDriver(),
  runtimeDriverFactory: createNodeRuntimeDriverFactory(),
  memoryLimit: 64, // MB
  cpuTimeLimitMs: 5000,
});
```

